            "tag": "br",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Languages:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Two of your choice"
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "br",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Equipment:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " A "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "disguise kit"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Value:25gp Weight:3lb"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", a set of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "fine clothes"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Value:15gp Weight:6lbs"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", and a belt pouch containing 30 gp."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Feature: Name Dropping"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You know and have met any number of powerful people across the land - and some of them might even remember you. You might be able to wrangle minor assistance from a major figure in the campaign, at the DM's discretion. Additionally, the common folk treat you with deference, and your heritage and the stories you tell might be good for a free meal or a place to sleep."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Suggested Characteristics"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Scions of celebrity adventurers must deal with fame that's not theirs, wealth they didn't earn. and expectations they can never hope to meet. These hardships can have adverse effects, but those who cope with them can arrive at a decent attitude and a grounded worldview. Those who fail become bitter - or worse."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h3",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Celebrity Adventurer's Scion Personality Trait"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "table",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "d8"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Personality Trait"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I will never get out of my famous parent's shadow, and no one else will ever understand this burden."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I've seen enough of the adventuring life to have realistic expectations and empathy for my peers."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Living up to my legacy will be difficult, but I'm going to do it."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I'm used to the very best in life, and that's a hard habit to break."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "My parent taught me a sense of duty. I strive to uphold it, even when the odds are against me."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "No one can fake a smile, a handshake, or an interested nod like I can."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "7"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I've been part of the adventuring life since I was old enough to walk. Let me explain a few things to you."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "8"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "No risk is too great for the rewards of defeating my enemies … and taking their stuff."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
